68
00:03:24,540 --> 00:03:25,500
(I love reading manga)

69
00:03:26,580 --> 00:03:28,860
(and fond of a manga artist
named Bodhi Leaf.)

70
00:03:28,860 --> 00:03:29,700
(Are you okay?)

71
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:32,740
(Stop!)
(Her stories always have strange twists.)

72
00:03:33,100 --> 00:03:34,740
(They really resonate with me.)

73
00:03:39,020 --> 00:03:40,580
Ye Ran, 26 years old,

74
00:03:40,580 --> 00:03:42,460
joined the head office's design team
two years ago.

75
00:03:42,860 --> 00:03:44,220
(Ye Ran)
This is her initial interview data.

76
00:03:44,380 --> 00:03:46,020
