85
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,980
Then which one did you produce yesterday?

86
00:04:17,740 --> 00:04:18,580
Oh no.

87
00:04:19,460 --> 00:04:21,420
You haven't sent the email yet, have you?

88
00:04:21,900 --> 00:04:23,340
I not only offended the boss,

89
00:04:23,820 --> 00:04:24,900
but also made the wrong poster.

90
00:04:26,060 --> 00:04:28,180
I am truly doomed.

91
00:04:30,340 --> 00:04:31,980
Is the poster ready?

92
00:04:32,060 --> 00:04:34,860
Mr. Meng, Manager Hao has
sent the poster to your email.

93
00:04:35,980 --> 00:04:36,820
Hao.

94
00:04:40,100 --> 00:04:42,340
(@Ye Ran, Interactive Entertainment)

95
00:04:43,260 --> 00:04:44,100
Manager Hao,

96
00:04:45,060 --> 00:04:46,060
why is this poster

97
00:04:46,460 --> 00:04:48,380
different from
the marketing department's proposal?

98
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:50,860
Just some minor adjustments.

99
00:04:56,380 --> 00:04:59,380
Boss, there're just a few slight adjustments.

100
00:04:59,660 --> 00:05:00,620
What's wrong with Ye Ran?

101
00:05:01,020 --> 00:05:02,060
- Quickly call her over.
- (Ye Ran?)

102
00:05:02,580 --> 00:05:03,700
(That's Bodhi Leaf.)

103
00:05:03,740 --> 00:05:05,000
She has to apologize for this.

104
00:05:05,170 --> 00:05:06,010
(No way.)

105
00:05:07,980 --> 00:05:09,860
I think the one who needs to apologize is you.

106
00:05:12,260 --> 00:05:13,100
The content of the poster

107
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:15,660
was planned by the marketing department.

108
00:05:16,420 --> 00:05:17,580
She's just a designer,

109
00:05:17,980 --> 00:05:19,020
responsible for execution.

110
00:05:20,100 --> 00:05:21,580
If she made a mistake with the poster,

111
00:05:22,060 --> 00:05:24,580
it means that you didn't accurately
convey the requirements

112
00:05:25,380 --> 00:05:27,220
or even provided incorrect information.

113
00:05:30,220 --> 00:05:31,060
Yes, yes, yes.

114
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:32,180
Boss, it's my fault.

115
00:05:32,460 --> 00:05:33,700
I'll talk with Ye Ran right away.

116
00:05:33,740 --> 00:05:34,580
Tonight,

117
00:05:34,940 --> 00:05:35,780
