123
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,660
- Secretary Chen.
- Yes, yes, yes.

124
00:05:49,900 --> 00:05:52,100
Reschedule the meeting
for the day after tomorrow.

125
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:55,260
Give the design team two days
to redo the poster.

126
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:57,220
- That's all.
- Okay, boss.

127
00:06:05,140 --> 00:06:05,980
(No.)

128
00:06:06,300 --> 00:06:07,740
(I need to send an email to Ye Ran.)

129
00:06:08,660 --> 00:06:11,100
The meeting is rescheduled
for the day after tomorrow.

130
00:06:11,580 --> 00:06:13,340
Submit the new poster
before the end of tomorrow.

131
00:06:19,620 --> 00:06:21,100
